<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Basque_Country_location_map.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Location of the Basque provinces within Spain and France</div>
</div>
