<p><a name="Examples" id="Examples"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Basque_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Examples">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Examples</span></h3>
<table>
<tr>
<td>
<p><b>The blacksmith slave</b><br />
Captive in the rainforests of the West<br />
they brought you to Rome, slave,<br />
they gave you the blacksmith work<br />
and you make chains.<br />
The red iron that you carry out the oven<br />
can be adapted as you want,<br />
you can make swords<br />
in order that your people could break the chains,<br />
but you, this slave,<br />
you make chains, more chains.<br />
:<a href="/wiki/Joseba_Sarrionandia" title="Joseba Sarrionandia">Joseba Sarrionandia</a></p>
</td>
<td>
<p><b>Esklabu erremintaria</b><br />
Sartaldeko oihanetan gatibaturik<br />
erromara ekarri zinduten, esklabua,<br />
erremintari ofizioa eman zizuten<br />
eta kateak egiten dituzu.<br />
Labetik ateratzen duzun burdin goria<br />
nahieran molda zenezake,<br />
ezpatak egin ditzakezu<br />
zure herritarrek kateak hauts deitzaten,<br />
baina zuk, esklabu horrek,<br />
kateak egiten dituzu, kate gehiago.<br />
:<a href="http://eu.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseba_Sarrionandia" class="extiw" title="eu:Joseba Sarrionandia">Joseba Sarrionandia</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
