<p><a name="Etymological_dictionaries" id="Etymological_dictionaries"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Basque_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Etymological dictionaries">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Etymological dictionaries</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>M. Löpelmann, Etymologisches Wörterbuch der baskischen Sprache, Berlin, 1968.</li>
<li>R.L. Trask <a href="http://www.sussex.ac.uk/linguistics/documents/lxwp23-08_edb.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.sussex.ac.uk/linguistics/documents/lxwp23-08_edb.pdf" rel="nofollow">Etymological Dictionary of Basque</a> edited for web publication by Max W. Wheeler (University of Sussex, 2008). An edition of the unfinished etymological dictionary of the late <a href="/wiki/Larry_Trask" title="Larry Trask">R. L. Trask</a>.</li>
</ul>
