<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.people.fas.harvard.edu/~witzel/mt26s.html" class="external text" title="http://www.people.fas.harvard.edu/~witzel/mt26s.html" rel="nofollow">A Final (?) Response to the Basque Debate in Mother Tongue 1</a> (John D. Bengston)</li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.germanistik.uni-muenchen.de/germanistische_linguistik/TV/Vennemann.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.germanistik.uni-muenchen.de/germanistische_linguistik/TV/Vennemann.htm" rel="nofollow">Theo Vennemann homepage</a></li>
