<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.ehu.es/grammar/gram42.htm#1.4.2.2.%20%20Potential%20paradigms:%20absolut" class="external text" title="http://www.ehu.es/grammar/gram42.htm#1.4.2.2.%20%20Potential%20paradigms:%20absolut" rel="nofollow">(Basque) INFLECTION §1.4.2.2. Potential paradigms: absolutive and dative.</a></li>
